Details.Education:
n lieu of specialized experience, you may qualify with the following education or combination of both education and experience: A Master's or equivalent graduate degree;
OR
Two full years of progressively higher level graduate education leading to a Master's or equivalent degree;
OR
An LL.B. or J.D., in a field directly related to the position being filled. A transcript must be submitted with your application if qualifying using education. See Required Documents for additional information.
